<li>Akerlof, George. "Thoughts on global warming." chinadialogue (2006). 14 July 2008. <a href="http://www.chinadialogue.net/article/show/single/en/143-Thoughts-on-global-warming" class="external free" title="http://www.chinadialogue.net/article/show/single/en/143-Thoughts-on-global-warming" rel="nofollow">http://www.chinadialogue.net/article/show/single/en/143-Thoughts-on-global-warming</a></li>
